      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for daily commuting or longer trips. While the exterior looks great overall, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light interior wear consistent with its age. All major systems are functional, and it has a clean service history, offering a great balance of quality and value for its next owner.",
