    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. While it shows some light, expected signs of use, it remains a dependable and attractive choice for any driver looking for quality and value. Ready for many more miles of adventure!",
